ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 196, Quebec
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 196 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of QUEBEC, with respect to the SPRING FLOOD, that affected the province from April, 2014 to May 20, 2014.
